title: Magic 2015 - Duels of the Planeswalkers
description:
Genre: Strategy

Start a great hunt in the Magic 2015-Duels of the Planeswalkers! Encourage powerful beings and bring down spells on the enemy.

Improve your skills in battle. But know this: you are stalking a dangerous enemy. Garruk Dikorechivy was the victim of a curse Chain Mail Veil. Locate and stop it!

System requirements
Operating system: Windows XP (SP3) / Windows Vista (SP2) / Windows 7 (SP1) / Windows 8 / Windows 8.1
Processor : CPU with 2 Ghz (starting from the Pentium 4) +
RAM: 1 GB RAM (only XP) 2 GB RAM (Vista, 7, 8)
HDD: 2 GB
Video Card: ATI or NVidia card with 512 MB ??RAM (with support for Shader 3.0)



By Doug Stamper.
